Pssh.

17
00:00:44,753 --> 00:00:46,505
Hey, you want to
bump baby lumps?

18
00:00:46,588 --> 00:00:48,135
Sick. No.

19
00:00:48,215 --> 00:00:50,058
Just try to follow
the plans, okay?

20
00:00:50,133 --> 00:00:50,929
Yeah.

21
